title: Postfix: Mailqueue Status
agents: linux
catalog: app/postfix
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the status of postfix mail instances on linux hosts.

 The status is OK if the mail instance is running, otherwise CRIT.

item:
 The name of the queue if multi instance is configured.

discovery:
 One service is created for each instance.
